{"content":"1130:      * Commit offsets synchronously. This method will retry until the commit completes successfully
1131:      * or an unrecoverable error is encountered.
1132:      * @param offsets The offsets to be committed
1133:      * @throws org.apache.kafka.common.errors.AuthorizationException if the consumer is not authorized to the group
1134:      *             or to any of the specified partitions. See the exception for more details
1135:      * @throws CommitFailedException if an unrecoverable error occurs before the commit can be completed
1136:      * @throws FencedInstanceIdException if a static member gets fenced
1137:      * @return If the offset commit was successfully sent and a successful response was received from
1138:      *         the coordinator
1139:      */
1140:     public boolean commitOffsetsSync(Map<TopicPartition, OffsetAndMetadata> offsets, Timer timer) {
1141:         invokeCompletedOffsetCommitCallbacks();
1142: 
1143:         if (offsets.isEmpty()) {
1144:             // We guarantee that the callbacks for all commitAsync() will be invoked when
1145:             // commitSync() completes, even if the user tries to commit empty offsets.
1146:             return invokePendingAsyncCommits(timer);
1147:         }
1148: 
1149:         long attempts = 0L;
1150:         do {
1151:             if (coordinatorUnknownAndUnreadySync(timer)) {
1152:                 return false;
1153:             }
1154: 
1155:             RequestFuture<Void> future = sendOffsetCommitRequest(offsets);
1156:             client.poll(future, timer);
1157: 
1158:             // We may have had in-flight offset commits when the synchronous commit began. If so, ensure that
1159:             // the corresponding callbacks are invoked prior to returning in order to preserve the order that
1160:             // the offset commits were applied.
1161:             invokeCompletedOffsetCommitCallbacks();
1162: 
1163:             if (future.succeeded()) {
1164:                 if (interceptors != null)
1165:                     interceptors.onCommit(offsets);
1166:                 return true;
1167:             }
1168: 
1169:             if (future.failed() && !future.isRetriable())
1170:                 throw future.exception();
1171: 
1172:             timer.sleep(retryBackoff.backoff(attempts++));
1173:         } while (timer.notExpired());
1174: 
1175:         return false;
1176:     }
